F.I.R.E. RESOURCES, INC., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
FELTRIM TUSCANY PRESERVE, LLC, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3737 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 07, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The parties' joint stipulation of dismissal is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is granted, with the appeal being dismissed. The pending amended status report and motion to extend abeyance period is denied as moot.
